{"tid":775260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"絕對唔買冇標明價錢嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-08-11T04:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T05:17:40.000Z","uid":77473,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1da67531953f4ccc6e1f6b3689e357f72cb698","tid":775260,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"你話我窮撚又好點又好 <br />\n同一個質素的話 點解明知畀人呃都中個頭埋去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔標明價錢嘅得兩種目的<br />\n<br />\n1.唔畀你格價  <br />\n  咁怕格價啫係專賣貴嘢 咁啫係我行多幾間一定有平啲嘅Choice <br />\n<br />\n2.想收海鮮價 新客舊客唔同價 <br />\n  又係劏新客啦 收皮啦 <br />\n<br />\n例子：朗豪坊魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74210e85eb5281378ce517be5f6e3970c49711b0","tid":775260,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"借刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfb956f4c6e9ec88b5f60402d1a2c0b63c4d718","tid":775260,"uid":27729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"其實好多舖頭都唔標明價錢<br />\n下下都要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我問得多又厭我煩<br />\n幾時打擊到呢種風氣"},{"pid":"9be342ed953a3089aa2ff0929449465d6f2d5f30","tid":775260,"uid":7996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"有好多網上賣野都唔出埋個價錢 <br />\n 要你pm佢再比個價你 呢啲都係好明顯想呃你一筆啦 <br />\n好地地唔可以打埋個價錢出黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a7e89c4b993f80c820a8ea39512c38233a6da2","tid":775260,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"咁揾工呢"},{"pid":"d73e7248d983ddd6d462bac44a5723a731a4a1e9","tid":775260,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68a7e89c4b993f80c820a8ea39512c38233a6da2","tid":775260,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"咁揾工呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"可比較性=0"}]}